text: Zhu Aiwen (; ; born 22 September 1994), also known as Angelina Zhu, is a Chinese tennis player. Zhu has a career high WTA singles ranking of 738 achieved on 5 November 2012. She also has a career high WTA doubles ranking of 395 achieved on 12 May 2014. Zhu has won 3 ITF doubles titles on the tour.
